## Messages shown to Pacified players when they try to do violence:

# With projectiles:
pacified-cannot-throw = 我无法扔出{ THE($projectile) }，那可能会伤到人！
# With embedding projectiles:
pacified-cannot-throw-embed = 我绝对不能扔出{ THE($projectile) }，那可能会刺入某人体内！
# With liquid-spilling projectiles:
pacified-cannot-throw-spill = 我不可能扔出{ THE($projectile) }，那可能会把恶心的东西溅到某人身上！

pacified-cannot-harm-directly = 我无法对{ THE($entity) }造成伤害！
pacified-cannot-harm-indirect = 我无法破坏{ THE($entity) }，那可能会伤到人！
pacified-cannot-fire-gun = 我无法开枪{ THE($entity) }，那可能会伤到人！
